description:
On today’s show, Emily is joined by host of The Jordan Harbinger Show Podcast  – you guessed it – Jordan Harbinger.

They talk about ways to maintain your work and romantic relationships in a healthy way from body language to staying your honest and authentic self, and why confidence is always key.
